---
title: Beyond Meat® and Pesto Flatbreads with Balsamic-Dressed Garden Salad
description: Beyond Meat® sautéed with onions is the perfect topper for pesto flatbreads! Finish with a sprinkling of mozzarella and Parmesan before transferring it to the oven for some melting action. A refreshing salad drizzled with balsamic glaze rounds out this delicious dinner.
